 74     output  rX
 78     input   [dc++]
 79     output  [dc++]
 7a
 7b
 7c
 7d
 7e     cfg-set 0xXX
 7f     cfg-clr 0xXX

 80     add     rX, { rX / 0xXX }
 90     addc    rX, { rX / 0xXX }
 a0     sub     rX, { rX / 0xXX }
 b0     subc    rX, { rX / 0xXX }
 c0     and     rX, { rX / 0xXX }
 d0     or      rX, { rX / 0xXX }
 e0     xor     rX, { rX / 0xXX }
 f0     cmp     rX, { rX / 0xXX }
--------

Configuration register:
 0 - I/O Device bit 0
 1 - I/O Device bit 1
 2 - I/O Device bit 2
 3 - I/O device bit 3
 4 - unused
 5 - ROM/RAM
 6 - Halt
 7 - Reset

--------

 Instruction-set improvements:
 Test by calculating and bcd-converting 10 Fibonacci numbers
 1451 - Starting point
 1401 - Add a 20s loop for BCD conversion
 1326 - add immediate
 1281 - sub immediate
 1038 - immediate support for remaining ALU instructions
